      "updated": 1775928195812,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Howw to start:\n\n(easy Way)\n\n- Create a K8s Cluster\n-Create the demployment\n-Create a Service -> Loadbalancer etc etc\n-Add a CNAME to the LB.\n\n(Harder Way):\n-Create a K8s cluster\n-Create a deployment\n-Create a service -> ClusterIP\n-Create/Update the ingress\n-Add a Certifcate\n- Update the Dns record.",
      "fontSize": 22.666666666666657,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Howw to start:\n\n(easy Way)\n\n- Create a K8s Cluster\n-Create the demployment\n-Create a Service -> Loadbalancer etc etc\n-Add a CNAME to the LB.\n\n(Harder Way):\n-Create a K8s cluster\n-Create a deployment\n-Create a service -> ClusterIP\n-Create/Update the ingress\n-Add a Certifcate\n- Update the Dns record.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
